title: PBR Handpainted Environment : Forest
description: The best  stylized handpainted fantasy assets to create beautiful fantasy nature environments in minutes!
longDescription:
Trailer


Discord | Facebook | Twitter | Email | Forum | Demo

Â A large collection of stylized handpainted PBR fantasy props to create a colorful fantasy nature environment in minutes. Features a unique stylized look that combines manual texture painting with modern PBR workflows to achieve a handpainted look. Can be used for Exploration, Adventure, RPG games and more. Suitable for first person, third person or even top down games.

This pack already contains over 95 stylized assets to jump-start the creation of any fantasy environment with more to come. It contains birch trees, oaks, cliffs and much more.


Want a campsite to place in your lush forest? Check out our PBR Magical Campsite pack.

Want some awesome fire VFX? Check out our Stylized VFX Collection : Fire pack!
technicalDetails:
Update 3

  • Added 16 grass types. Added 4 new tree types & 4 new rock types. Added 2 terrain meshes & 4 terrain billboards.
  • Reworked tree models & textures, grass & flower textures & leaf textures


Features:

  • 95 stylized assets including foliage and props.
  • 3 Stylized Particle Effects.
  • 4 Background terrain billboards
  • 2 Stylized water textures.
  • 6 stylized handpainted pbr omnidirectional tiling terrain textures.
  • Optimized geometry and lightmaps.
  • Can be used both in PBR and non-PBR workflows.

Texture Sizes:

  • 4096(For the larger props)
  • 2048(90% of the assets)
  • 1024(tiling terrain textures)
  • 512

Collision:

  • Custom collision for the majority of assets. Per poly and simple for a few where it did not make sense to make custom.

Vertex Count: Between 200- 15000

LODs: Between 1 and 4

Number of Meshes:89

Number of Materials and Material Instances: 103

Number of Textures: 160

Supported Development Platforms: Any

Supported Target Build Platforms: Any non mobile (assets render fine but the terrain is too complex)
